headline: Duke Energy supports western North Carolina recovery efforts with $500,000 in grants to local nonprofits
summary: As part of its commitment to supporting a full recovery in western North Carolina following Hurricane Helene, Duke Energy Foundation today announced $500,000 in new funding to 20 local nonprofits.
